[[DEVONagent|https://www.devontechnologies.com/apps/devonagent]] is an amazing search software developed by [[DEVONtechnologies]].

I've set up many different Plugins and Search sets to search common blogs I read. It's also a great tool to search different forums posting sites due to its ability to crawl the pages independently of a search engine.

DEVONagent unfortunately doesn't search TiddlyWiki's but that is limitation of TiddlyWiki not having a default sitemap.xml.